{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "6. Eſkanus/ un Jeſius/ un\nAsareêls/ un Joëſers/ un Jaſa-\nbeams/ tas Koriteris.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "7. Un Joëlus/ un Sabadijuſ/\nJeroatta Dehti no Gedoraſ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "8. No teem Gaditexeim\nSchkihrahſ arridsan pee Dahwi-\ndu us to Stiprumu Tuftneſi/\nwarreni Karra-Wihri/ kaſ\npreekschturramas Bruknas un\nSchkehpus walkaja/ un winnu\nWaigi bija ka Lautou Waigi/\nun tee bija tik schigli ka Stirnas\nus Kalneem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "9. Tas augstakajs bija Ee-\nfers/ un tas ohtre Obadijuſ/ tas\ntrefchajs Elijabſ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "10. Tas zettortajs Masman-\nnus/ tas peektajs Jeremijus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "11. Tas ſestajs Atajus/ tas\nſeptitajs Eliêls.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "12. Tas aſtotajs Joaans/\ntas dewitajs Elſabads.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "13. Tas deſmitajs Jeremi-\njuſ/ tas weenpadeſmitajs Mak-\nbanajus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "14. Schee bija no Gada Behr-\nneem/ Karra-Wirſneeki/ weens\nno teem Masakajeem bija pahr\nſimteem/ un weens leelakajs bija\npahr tubkſtoscheem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "15. Schee irr tee/ kaſ pahr to\nJardanu gahje pirma Mehneſi/\nkad tas pils bija wiſtas taiwa\nMalläs. Un tee iſdſinne wiſius\nEeleijas Laudis/ prett Rihteem\nun prett Wakkarnuſi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "16. No teem Behrneem Ju-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "17. Un Dahwidg tsgahje teeu\npretti/ un atbildēja/ un fazzija\nus teem: Ja juhs Meera peh-\npee mañim effat nahkufchi/ man\npalihdſeht/ tad buhs manna\nSirđs ta patt ar jums/ bet ja\ntas tapehz irr/ ka juhs manna\nWiltu gribbat manneem Eenaids\nneekeem eedoht/ fur tomehr ne\nkahda Blehdiba pee mann irr/\ntad laid muhfu Tehwu Deewa\nto reds/ un fołda.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "18. Bet tas Gars apgehrbe\nAlmasaju to Ahwerſtu starp teeu\nWirfneekem : (un tas fazzija:\nMehs teiw peederram Dahwids/\nun ar teiw buhſim mehs tu Dehls\nIsaja/Meers/ Meers lai irr ar\ntew/ un Meers ar taweein Pa-\nligeem/ jo taws Deews irr taws\nPaligs. Tad preezehme tohs\nDahwids/ un eezehele tohs par\nWirfneekem pahr teem Karra-\nPulkeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "19. Ir no Manaſsus pahr-\ngahje pee Dahwida/ kad tas nah-\nze ar teem Willſtereen prett\nSaulu karroht/ un teem ne pa-\nlihdſeja/ jo tee Willſtern Leeli-\nRungi atlaiđe to ar Padohnm/\ntazzidami : Wiſch pee fawu\nRungu Saulu pahrees ar muhfu\nGalwu (Noſufchanu).\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "20. Kad wiſch us Ziklagu\ngahje/ tad peemettehs pee ta no\nManaſsus/ Adnaks un Josa-\nbads/ un Jedtaels/ un Mikaels/\nun Josabads/ un Elijus/ un Zil-\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
